---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Broker de Hipotecas en Miami | Mister Mortgage USA | NMLS #2572035"
  description="Mister Mortgage USA — el broker hipotecario de confianza en Miami. FHA, VA, USDA, Jumbo, Tasa Fija y más. Asesoría experta, aprobaciones rápidas. NMLS #2572035. Llama (305) 615-1515."
  lang="es"
  canonical="https://mistermortgageusa.com/es"
  altLang="/"
  hasMap={true}
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section id="hero" aria-label="Hero">
    <div class="hero-bg" id="hero-bg">
      <img class="hero-slide active" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1533395427226-788cee25cc7b?w=1600&q=80&fit=crop" alt="Skyline de Miami Brickell" loading="eager" />
      <img class="hero-slide" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600607687939-ce8a6c25118c?w=1600&q=80&fit=crop" alt="Casa de lujo moderna en Miami" loading="lazy" />
      <img class="hero-slide" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605146769289-440113cc3d00?w=1600&q=80&fit=crop" alt="Arquitectura moderna de Miami" loading="lazy" />
      <img class="hero-slide" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512917774080-9991f1c4c750?w=1600&q=80&fit=crop" alt="Casa en el sur de Florida" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-left">
        <div class="hero-badge"><span class="hero-badge-dot"></span><span data-i18n="hero.badge">El Broker Hipotecario de Confianza en Miami</span></div>
        <h1 class="hero-h1" data-i18n="hero.h1">Obtén las mejores<br/><em>tasas hipotecarias</em><br/>hoy</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub" data-i18n="hero.sub">Antes de comenzar a buscar tu primera casa — déjanos ayudarte a precalificarte para tu hipoteca. Asesoría experta, aprobaciones rápidas y servicio personalizado.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn btn-red" href="#" onclick="openPrequalModal();return false;">
            <span data-i18n="hero.btn.prequal">PRECALIFÍQUESE AHORA</span>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
          <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/es/opciones-de-prestamo"><span data-i18n="hero.btn.explore">Ver Opciones de Préstamo</span></a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-trust">
          <div class="hero-trust-item"><div class="hero-trust-num">20+</div><div class="hero-trust-label" data-i18n="hero.trust.exp">Años de Experiencia</div></div>
          <div class="hero-trust-item"><div class="hero-trust-num">NMLS</div><div class="hero-trust-label">#2572035</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-right">
        <div class="hero-img-wrap">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600607687939-ce8a6c25118c?w=800&q=80&fit=crop" alt="Casa moderna en Miami" />
          <div class="hero-img-badge"><span>$1B+</span><span>In Loans Closed</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LOANS CAROUSEL -->
  <section id="loans-preview" aria-label="Loan programs">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label reveal" data-i18n="loans.label">Programas de Préstamo</span>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1" data-i18n="loans.title">Encuentra el Préstamo <em>Correcto para Ti</em></h2>
        <div class="red-line" style="margin:1.25rem auto;"></div>
        <p class="section-subtitle reveal reveal-delay-2" style="margin:0 auto;" data-i18n="loans.subtitle">Desde compradores primerizos hasta inversores experimentados, ofrecemos 10 programas adaptados a tu situación financiera.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="loans-carousel-wrap">
        <div class="loans-carousel">
          <div class="loans-track" id="loans-track">
            <div class="loan-slide"><div class="loan-card" onclick="openLoanModal(0)"><div class="loan-card-img"><img src="/images/loans/fixed-rate.jpg" alt="Hipoteca de Tasa Fija" loading="lazy" /></div><span class="loan-chip" data-i18n="loan.chip.popular">Más Popular</span><div class="loan-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="loans.card.fixed.title">Hipoteca de Tasa Fija</h3><p data-i18n="loan.short.fixed">Asegura un pago constante que nunca cambia. Ideal para compradores que valoran la estabilidad.</p><div class="loan-cta-hint"><span data-i18n="loan.cta.learn">Más información</span> <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></div></div></div>
            <div class="loan-slide"><div class="loan-card" onclick="openLoanModal(1)"><div class="loan-card-img"><img src="/images/loans/fha.jpg" alt="Préstamo FHA" loading="lazy" /></div><span class="loan-chip" data-i18n="loan.lowdown">Bajo Pago Inicial</span><div class="loan-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 10.5L12 3l9 7.5V21H15v-6H9v6H3V10.5z"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="loans.card.fha.title">Préstamo FHA</h3><p data-i18n="loan.short.fha">Financiamiento respaldado por el gobierno con pagos iniciales desde 3.5%. Perfecto para puntajes de crédito moderados.</p><div class="loan-cta-hint"><span data-i18n="loan.cta.learn">Más información</span> <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></div></div></div>
            <div class="loan-slide"><div class="loan-card" onclick="openLoanModal(2)"><div class="loan-card-img"><img src="/images/loans/va.jpg" alt="Préstamo VA" loading="lazy" /></div><span class="loan-chip" data-i18n="loan.chip.zerodown">Sin Pago Inicial</span><div class="loan-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="loans.card.va.title">Préstamo VA</h3><p data-i18n="loan.short.va">Beneficios exclusivos para veteranos y militares en servicio activo — sin pago inicial, sin PMI.</p><div class="loan-cta-hint"><span data-i18n="loan.cta.learn">Más información</span> <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></div></div></div>
            <div class="loan-slide"><div class="loan-card" onclick="openLoanModal(3)"><div class="loan-card-img"><img src="/images/loans/usda.jpg" alt="Préstamo USDA Florida" loading="lazy" /></div><span class="loan-chip" data-i18n="loan.chip.zerodown">Sin Pago Inicial</span><div class="loan-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="loans.card.usda.title">Préstamo USDA Florida</h3><p data-i18n="loan.short.usda">Financiamiento al 100% para propiedades rurales y suburbanas elegibles. Sin pago inicial.</p><div class="loan-cta-hint"><span data-i18n="loan.cta.learn">Más información</span> <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></div></div></div>
            <div class="loan-slide"><div class="loan-card" onclick="openLoanModal(4)"><div class="loan-card-img"><img src="/images/loans/jumbo.jpg" alt="Préstamos Jumbo Miami" loading="lazy" /></div><span class="loan-chip" data-i18n="loan.chip.luxury">Lujo</span><div class="loan-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="loans.card.jumbo.title">Préstamos Jumbo Miami</h3><p data-i18n="loan.short.jumbo">Financiamiento para propiedades de alto valor que superan los límites de préstamos convencionales.</p><div class="loan-cta-hint"><span data-i18n="loan.cta.learn">Más información</span> <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></div></div></div>
            <div class="loan-slide"><div class="loan-card" onclick="openLoanModal(5)"><div class="loan-card-img"><img src="/images/loans/first-time-buyer.jpg" alt="Primer Comprador de Casa" loading="lazy" /></div><span class="loan-chip" data-i18n="loan.chip.ftb">Primer Comprador</span><div class="loan-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H6a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="loans.card.ftb.title">Primer Comprador de Casa</h3><p data-i18n="loan.short.ftb">Orientación especializada y programas para compradores primerizos, incluyendo asistencia para el pago inicial.</p><div class="loan-cta-hint"><span data-i18n="loan.cta.learn">Más información</span> <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></div></div></div>
            <div class="loan-slide"><div class="loan-card" onclick="openLoanModal(6)"><div class="loan-card-img"><img src="/images/loans/low-down-payment.jpg" alt="Bajo Pago Inicial" loading="lazy" /></div><span class="loan-chip" data-i18n="loan.chip.3down">Desde 3% de Entrada</span><div class="loan-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm1.41 16.09V20h-2.67v-1.93c-1.71-.36-3.16-1.46-3.27-3.4h1.96c.1 1.05.82 1.87 2.65 1.87 1.96 0 2.4-.98 2.4-1.59 0-.83-.44-1.61-2.67-2.14-2.48-.6-4.18-1.62-4.18-3.67 0-1.72 1.39-2.84 3.11-3.21V4h2.67v1.95c1.86.45 2.79 1.86 2.85 3.39H14.3c-.05-1.11-.64-1.87-2.22-1.87-1.5 0-2.4.68-2.4 1.64 0 .84.65 1.39 2.67 1.91s4.18 1.39 4.18 3.91c-.01 1.83-1.38 2.83-3.12 3.16z"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="loans.card.lowdown.title">Bajo Pago Inicial</h3><p data-i18n="loan.short.lowdown">Opciones de compra con tan solo 3% de entrada. Te ayudamos a navegar todos los programas disponibles.</p><div class="loan-cta-hint"><span data-i18n="loan.cta.learn">Más información</span> <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></div></div></div>
            <div class="loan-slide"><div class="loan-card" onclick="openLoanModal(7)"><div class="loan-card-img"><img src="/images/loans/rehab-203k.jpg" alt="Préstamo Rehab 203k" loading="lazy" /></div><span class="loan-chip" data-i18n="loan.chip.renovate">Compra &amp; Renueva</span><div class="loan-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 000 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 001.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 01-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 01-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 017.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="loans.card.rehab.title">Préstamos Rehab (203k)</h3><p data-i18n="loan.short.rehab">Financia la compra de tu casa y los costos de renovación en una sola hipoteca.</p><div class="loan-cta-hint"><span data-i18n="loan.cta.learn">Más información</span> <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></div></div></div>
            <div class="loan-slide"><div class="loan-card" onclick="openLoanModal(8)"><div class="loan-card-img"><img src="/images/loans/investment.jpg" alt="Préstamos para Inversión" loading="lazy" /></div><span class="loan-chip" data-i18n="loan.chip.wealth">Construye Riqueza</span><div class="loan-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="loans.card.invest.title">Préstamos para Inversión</h3><p data-i18n="loan.short.invest">Construye independencia financiera a través del mercado inmobiliario del sur de Florida.</p><div class="loan-cta-hint"><span data-i18n="loan.cta.learn">Más información</span> <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></div></div></div>
            <div class="loan-slide"><div class="loan-card" onclick="openLoanModal(9)"><div class="loan-card-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-6726b3ff858f?w=400&q=75&fit=crop" alt="Refinanciamiento de Hipoteca" loading="lazy" /></div><span class="loan-chip" data-i18n="loan.chip.rate">Baja Tu Tasa</span><div class="loan-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="1 4 1 10 7 10"/><path d="M3.51 15a9 9 0 1 0 .49-3.61"/></svg></div><h3 data-i18n="loans.card.refi.title">Refinanciamiento</h3><p data-i18n="loan.short.refi">Reduce tu pago, accede a tu capital o acorta el plazo de tu préstamo.</p><div class="loan-cta-hint"><span data-i18n="loan.cta.learn">Más información</span> <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></div></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-nav">
          <button class="carousel-btn" id="carousel-prev" onclick="carouselPrev()" aria-label="Anterior"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/></svg></button>
          <div class="carousel-dots" id="carousel-dots"></div>
          <button class="carousel-btn" id="carousel-next" onclick="carouselNext()" aria-label="Siguiente"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg></button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="loans-cta" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">
        <a class="btn btn-red" href="/es/opciones-de-prestamo">
          <span data-i18n="loans.view.all">Ver las 10 Opciones de Préstamo</span>
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LOAN PROCESS TIMELINE -->
  <section id="loan-timeline" aria-label="Loan Process">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label reveal" data-i18n="timeline.label">Cómo Funciona</span>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1" data-i18n="timeline.title">Tu Camino hacia la <em>Casa Propia</em></h2>
        <div class="red-line" style="margin:1.25rem auto;"></div>
        <p class="section-subtitle reveal reveal-delay-2" style="margin:0 auto;" data-i18n="timeline.subtitle">Desde la primera llamada hasta el cierre — te guiamos en cada paso del proceso hipotecario.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-steps">
        <div class="timeline-step reveal">
          <div class="timeline-num"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/></svg></div>
          <span class="timeline-step-label" data-i18n="timeline.step1.label">Paso 1</span>
          <h4 data-i18n="timeline.step1.title">Precalificación</h4>
          <p data-i18n="timeline.step1.body">Evaluamos tu perfil financiero y te decimos exactamente para qué calificas — sin sorpresas.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="timeline-num"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/></svg></div>
          <span class="timeline-step-label" data-i18n="timeline.step2.label">Paso 2</span>
          <h4 data-i18n="timeline.step2.title">Solicitud</h4>
          <p data-i18n="timeline.step2.body">Envía tu solicitud con nuestro proceso guiado. Lo hacemos simple y sin estrés.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="timeline-num"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg></div>
          <span class="timeline-step-label" data-i18n="timeline.step3.label">Paso 3</span>
          <h4 data-i18n="timeline.step3.title">Aprobación Rápida</h4>
          <p data-i18n="timeline.step3.body">Nuestro equipo trabaja rápido. La mayoría de los clientes recibe aprobación en días.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-step reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="timeline-num"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 10.5L12 3l9 7.5V21H15v-6H9v6H3V10.5z"/></svg></div>
          <span class="timeline-step-label" data-i18n="timeline.step4.label">Paso 4</span>
          <h4 data-i18n="timeline.step4.title">Día de Cierre</h4>
          <p data-i18n="timeline.step4.body">Firma los documentos y recibe las llaves. Estaremos a tu lado hasta que seas oficialmente propietario.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:3rem;">
        <a class="btn btn-red reveal reveal-delay-4" href="#" onclick="openPrequalModal();return false;">
          <span data-i18n="timeline.cta">Comienza Tu Camino Hoy</span>
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- NEIGHBORHOODS MAP -->
  <section id="neighborhoods" aria-label="Neighborhoods We Serve">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label reveal" data-i18n="neighborhoods.label">Área de Servicio</span>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal reveal-delay-1" data-i18n="neighborhoods.title">Vecindarios que <em>Servimos</em></h2>
        <div class="red-line" style="margin:1.25rem auto;"></div>
        <p class="section-subtitle reveal reveal-delay-2" style="margin:0 auto;" data-i18n="neighborhoods.subtitle">Conocemos el sur de Florida — desde condominios en Brickell hasta compradores primerizos en Homestead, tenemos un préstamo para cada vecindario.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="neighborhoods-grid reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div id="neighborhoods-map"></div>
        <div class="neighborhoods-list" id="neighborhoods-list">
          <div class="neighborhood-chip" onclick="focusNeighborhood(0)"><span class="neighborhood-chip-dot"></span><span><strong>Brickell</strong><span class="neighborhood-chip-type">Condos &amp; Inversión</span></span></div>
          <div class="neighborhood-chip" onclick="focusNeighborhood(1)"><span class="neighborhood-chip-dot"></span><span><strong>Coral Gables</strong><span class="neighborhood-chip-type">Residencial Premium</span></span></div>
          <div class="neighborhood-chip" onclick="focusNeighborhood(2)"><span class="neighborhood-chip-dot"></span><span><strong>Doral</strong><span class="neighborhood-chip-type">Primer Comprador</span></span></div>
          <div class="neighborhood-chip" onclick="focusNeighborhood(3)"><span class="neighborhood-chip-dot"></span><span><strong>Hialeah</strong><span class="neighborhood-chip-type">Programas FHA</span></span></div>
          <div class="neighborhood-chip" onclick="focusNeighborhood(4)"><span class="neighborhood-chip-dot"></span><span><strong>Kendall</strong><span class="neighborhood-chip-type">Familias Suburbanas</span></span></div>
          <div class="neighborhood-chip" onclick="focusNeighborhood(5)"><span class="neighborhood-chip-dot"></span><span><strong>Coconut Grove</strong><span class="neighborhood-chip-type">Propiedades de Lujo</span></span></div>
          <div class="neighborhood-chip" onclick="focusNeighborhood(6)"><span class="neighborhood-chip-dot"></span><span><strong>Aventura</strong><span class="neighborhood-chip-type">Condos &amp; Inversión</span></span></div>
          <div class="neighborhood-chip" onclick="focusNeighborhood(7)"><span class="neighborhood-chip-dot"></span><span><strong>Miami Beach</strong><span class="neighborhood-chip-type">Lujo e Internacional</span></span></div>
          <div class="neighborhood-chip" onclick="focusNeighborhood(8)"><span class="neighborhood-chip-dot"></span><span><strong>Homestead</strong><span class="neighborhood-chip-type">USDA &amp; FHA</span></span></div>
          <div class="neighborhood-chip" onclick="focusNeighborhood(9)"><span class="neighborhood-chip-dot"></span><span><strong>Pinecrest</strong><span class="neighborhood-chip-type">Casas de Alto Valor</span></span></div>
          <div class="neighborhood-chip" onclick="focusNeighborhood(10)"><span class="neighborhood-chip-dot"></span><span><strong>Westchester</strong><span class="neighborhood-chip-type">FHA &amp; Familias</span></span></div>
          <div class="neighborhood-chip" onclick="focusNeighborhood(11)"><span class="neighborhood-chip-dot"></span><span><strong>South Miami</strong><span class="neighborhood-chip-type">Residencial Mixto</span></span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-divider"></div>

  <!-- ABOUT SNIPPET -->
  <section id="about-snippet" aria-label="About us">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-img-wrap reveal">
        <img src="/images/about-us.jpg" alt="Consulta hipotecaria profesional" />
